Package tp_ed.capturetheflag.game

package tp_ed.capturetheflag.game
  • Class
    Description
    Algorithm
    Represents an algorithm used by a bot in the game.
    AlgorithmType
    Enumerates the types of algorithms that can be used by bots in the game.
    Bot
    The Bot class represents a bot in the game.
    Flag
    The Flag class represents a flag in the game.
    GameController
    The GameController class is responsible for managing the game's overall flow in Capture the Flag.
    GameMap
    The GameMap class represents the game map for the game.
    GameRules
    Contains utility methods for enforcing game rules and performing safe input operations in game.
    GameUtils
    The GameUtils class provides utility methods for gameplay mechanics in the game.
    Player
    The Player class represents a player in the game.
